1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 5=

3
00:00:15,912 --> 00:00:16,471
(Ministry of Justice, Gate Bureau)
Commissioner.

4
00:00:17,079 --> 00:00:18,719
Is Li Wan's autopsy report ready?

5
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,399
The palm strike
was clean and decisive.

6
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,719
A single, fatal blow.

7
00:00:30,359 --> 00:00:31,120
It appears

8
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,799
that Chu Yunchang knows martial art.

9
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,399
I also suspect that Li Wan

10
00:00:37,560 --> 00:00:39,799
wouldn't kidnap
a mere florist for no reason.

11
00:00:41,560 --> 00:00:43,719
Every major event in the Capital

12
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,280
is linked to the Grandmaster
of the Martial Alliance.

13
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:49,960
It seems we won't have answers
until the Queen Thief of the South

14
00:00:50,237 --> 00:00:51,477
finally makes her appearance.

15
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:53,880
Sect Leader!

16
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:54,719
What's the rush?

17
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,439
She is changing her bandages!

18
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,000
Speak!

19
00:00:57,190 --> 00:00:59,000
Lady Thousand-Hands
is forcing her way here.

20
00:00:59,050 --> 00:01:00,679
The two Guardians request your presence.

21
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:20,719
So, you are the Jade Squirrel.

22
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,239
What are you doing here?

23
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,079
I've come to issue a challenge.

24
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,400
A challenge?

25
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,879
I want a duel.

26
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,319
The winner

27
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,959
becomes the true
Grandmaster of the Martial Alliance.

28
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,519
Fine, you win.

29
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:42,560
You...

30
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:45,159
I've been looking
for an excuse to drop the title anyway.

31
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,400
If you want it,

32
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,599
I'll hand it over now.

33
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,480
Bye-bye.

34
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:49,799
Chu Yunchang!

35
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,959
You are far too arrogant!

36
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:54,319
Are you even being reasonable?

37
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,120
You came here to issue a challenge,

38
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,519
I forfeit, and you lost your temper?

39
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:01,439
You've left me no choice.

40
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,200
Why don't you take a look

41
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,840
(Northern Martial Alliance, Token)
at what this is?

42
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:09,375
(Token)

43
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,000
The Sacred Token!

44
00:02:14,487 --> 00:02:15,587
(Northern Martial Alliance, Token)

45
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,599
You aren't the first person

46
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:23,080
to wave a fake Sacred Token around.

47
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:24,879
You think it's a fake?

48
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:28,479
Then, I'll leave it
at Red Leaf Villa for three days.

49
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,240
If you don't come for it,

50
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:32,000
I'll hand it over to the Gate Bureau.

51
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:35,360
When the Sacred Hand Sect's
greatest treasure

52
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,479
falls into the hands of the Bureau,

53
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:40,120
you'll become the laughingstock
of the martial world.

54
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:42,680
I'd love to see
how you'll show your face

55
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:45,080
as the Grandmaster
of this Alliance then.

56
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:50,960
Chang!

57
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,120
I think the token
in that image was real.

58
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,230
If she truly had the real Sacred Token,

59
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:56,879
she would've commanded the world.

60
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,240
Chang!

61
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,190
Quickly, get a healer!

62
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:02,310
Chang!

63
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,240
No.

64
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:06,680
Lin Xin'er is still suspicious.

65
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,360
Her people must be
staking out the entrance.

66
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:11,240
I just need to lie down for a bit.

67
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:17,190
(A new lead
to the Sacred Token was revealed.)

68
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,800
(The Grandmaster is still recovering.)

69
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,520
(I'll scout Red Leaf Villa first.)

70
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:30,250
(Token)

71
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,080
(The Sacred Token really is here.)

72
00:03:34,412 --> 00:03:35,562
(Token)

73
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:55,479
Go.

74
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:57,560
Let's move.

75
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,700
Where is the antidote
for the Seven-Flower Toxin?

76
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:18,040
Since you refused my challenge,

77
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,279
I had to force your hand.

78
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,720
By the way,

79
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,079
where is Chu Yunchang?

80
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,160
Why isn't she coming out?

81
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,399
Is she scared?

82
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,160
To deal with you,

83
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:30,160
there's no need for the Grandmaster.

84
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,519
I am more than enough.

85
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,079
Hand over the antidote.

86
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,480
I've already placed it

87
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,399
in Prince Duan's Treasure Trove.

88
00:04:39,312 --> 00:04:40,112
Pick another place.

89
00:04:40,487 --> 00:04:41,286
I'll duel you.

90
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:43,160
I only duel Chu Yunchang.

91
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:48,040
Tell her that if she wants
to save Chu Xiangling's life,

92
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:50,519
she must get to the antidote before me,

93
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:52,480
by sunrise tomorrow.

94
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:53,959
Otherwise...

95
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:58,480
Chu Xiangling is as good as dead.

96
00:05:00,912 --> 00:05:03,637
(Chu's Residence)

97
00:05:05,519 --> 00:05:06,279
Sanbao?

98
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,519
Mistress.

99
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:09,720
Go send a message to the Gate Bureau.

100
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:13,240
Tell them the Jade Squirrel

101
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,680
is going to hit
Prince Duan's Residence tonight.

102
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:17,040
Understood.

103
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,040
Rong.

104
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,160
Our spies report

105
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,199
that the Jade Squirrel will hit

106
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:23,839
Prince Duan's Residence tonight.

107
00:05:23,839 --> 00:05:25,270
There will be chaos in the Capital.

108
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,040
Haven't you been saying

109
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,519
how guilty you feel toward Ms. Chu?

110
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:31,360
Here's a perfect chance to repay her.

111
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,399
You mean...

112
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,519
Ms. Chu is just a young woman,

113
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,959
and she's still injured.

114
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:39,260
It's not safe for her
to guard that flower shop alone.

115
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:41,759
Why don't you rush over there

116
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:43,199
and stay by her side all night?

117
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:44,639
Think of it as settling your debt.

118
00:05:45,212 --> 00:05:45,892
Wushuang,

119
00:05:45,892 --> 00:05:47,332
thank you for letting me know.

120
00:05:47,375 --> 00:05:48,174
I'll get changed

121
00:05:48,174 --> 00:05:48,854
and head there.

122
00:05:48,854 --> 00:05:49,414
Good.

123
00:05:52,737 --> 00:05:55,857
(Tonight, I am definitely
catching the Jade Squirrel.)

124
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,639
Miss,

125
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,519
Mao Buyu's sister is here to see you.

126
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,600
Rong? Why are you here?

127
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,439
Don't move.

128
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:08,160
Yunchang, I'm sorry.

129
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,560
You were hurt because of me.

130
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,790
It's only right that I visit you.

131
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,680
How are you feeling?

132
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,680
I'm fine now.

133
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,879
That's good.

134
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,680
This is top-tier scar ointment.

135
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,560
I hope it helps with your recovery.

136
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,800
Thank you.

137
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:23,480
(Is Mao Wenrong up to something?)

138
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:25,560
(She'd better not tell Chang
about the plan)

139
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,800
(at Prince Duan's Residence.)

140
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,480
You've seen her.

141
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,800
She's clearly doing fine.

142
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,920
You can leave now.

143
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,839
I'm in no rush.

144
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,800
I'm staying here with you tonight.

145
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,560
Why?

146
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,600
No!

147
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,720
Zhizhi.

148
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,439
What is wrong with you?

149
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,480
You've been acting strange all evening.

150
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,360
She must have heard about

151
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,500
what's happening
at Prince Duan's Residence tonight.

152
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,480
What's wrong with it?

153
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,000
It's getting late.

154
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:58,000
We should turn in early,
don't you think?

155
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,680
Rong,

156
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,800
did something happen at the residence?

157
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,990
The Jade Squirrel made a bet
with Lady Thousand-Hands.

158
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,320
He declared he would raid
Prince Duan's Residence tonight.

159
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,160
The entire city is now under lockdown.

160
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,360
That's their business.

161
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:12,920
What does it have to do with my sister?

162
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,480
She's currently bedridden with an injury

163
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,560
and needs her rest.

164
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,800
You shouldn't disturb her.

165
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,120
Buyu is out on a mission.

166
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,120
He's worried about your safety.

167
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,920
So, I will be staying here tonight

168
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,920
to protect you.

169
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,879
I'm not going anywhere.

170
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,560
Well,

171
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:30,519
I really don't like
being watched while I sleep.

172
00:07:30,775 --> 00:07:31,456
Perhaps

173
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:35,160
you should head back.

174
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,120
Exactly. You should leave.

175
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,560
Let my sister get some rest.

176
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,000
I'll just keep watch right beside you.

177
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,040
I won't make a sound.

178
00:07:42,537 --> 00:07:43,897
Your safety is at stake, Yunchang.

179
00:07:43,987 --> 00:07:45,266
Please, do not refuse.

180
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:53,470
I'm a bit tired
from the flower arranging earlier.

181
00:07:54,787 --> 00:07:56,148
I want to sleep for a while.

182
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,920
Zhizhi.

183
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,920
Light the incense for me.

184
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:02,319
I want to sleep peacefully.

185
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,160
Right away.

186
00:08:39,925 --> 00:08:41,875
(Prince Duan's Residence)

187
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,840
(Prince Duan's Residence)
We will surround the place and wait

188
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,600
for the target.

189
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,240
Do not alert them.

190
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,600
Yu,

191
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,759
it's going to be hard
not to alert anyone this time.

192
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,679
Everyone, look sharp!

193
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:04,320
Show them the might
of the Embroidered Guard!

194
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,960
(Embroidered Guard, Official Zhuang)
Official Zhuang, I presume?

195
00:09:13,399 --> 00:09:14,440
Look who we have here.

196
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,120
The Gate Bureau is hunting a thief.

197
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:18,080
Why is the Embroidered Guard here too?

198
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:21,120
His Highness Prince Duan
feared you lot were out of your depth.

199
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,440
He sent word to our Commander-in-Chief,

200
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:25,660
requesting that the Embroidered Guard
lead the operation.

201
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,679
Now that we've arrived,

202
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,799
you may clear out.

203
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,440
Not so fast.

204
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,799
Catching thieves

205
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,559
is the sole jurisdiction
of the Gate Bureau.

206
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,799
By surrounding the manor
with such a spectacle,

207
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:35,960
you're just alerting the target?

208
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,279
The thief will be ready.

209
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:42,100
I want them to know
who they're up against..

210
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,320
The Embroidered Guard
is holding the line here tonight.

211
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:48,000
If those thieves are truly suicidal,

212
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,799
let them try their luck.

213
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,480
Vice Commissioner.

214
00:09:57,020 --> 00:09:58,960
His Highness asks that
you lead your squad inside

215
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,840
to secure the Prince
and Princess's chambers.

216
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,720
What about our orders?

217
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:05,039
Chief Constable Yue,
lead your team to the Treasure Trove.

218
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:07,080
With the Embroidered Guard on site,

219
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,840
I see no reason to rely
on the Gate Bureau.

220
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,879
They are dead weight.

221
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:11,840
Move.

222
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,720
Right this way.

223
00:10:14,387 --> 00:10:16,912
(Treasure Trove)

224
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,320
Who goes there?

225
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,279
Stand down.

226
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,799
It's me.

227
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,660
- My respects, Your Highness.
- My respects, Your Highness.

228
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,000
Your Highness,

229
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,279
shouldn't you be

230
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:30,240
in the safe room?

231
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:31,175
(Prince Duan)

232
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,641
Because the Treasure Trove
weighs heavily on my mind.

233
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,360
These are imperial gifts.

234
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,039
I won't risk even a single scratch.

235
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,919
I need to verify the inventory myself.

236
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:40,679
But the thief

237
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,360
is targeting this chamber.

238
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,799
Inspecting it now

239
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,799
seems too risky.

240
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,360
Risky in what sense?

241
00:10:49,787 --> 00:10:51,125
(Treasure Trove)

242
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:51,879
Your Highness.

243
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,720
This is Prince Duan's Residence.

244
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:55,799
The Prince's own home.

245
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:57,080
If His Highness wishes to inspect

246
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,360
his own treasures,

247
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,440
how is that wrong?

248
00:11:00,170 --> 00:11:02,080
The Gate Bureau certainly
has a lot of bluster.

249
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,559
And quite a lot of nerve, too!

250
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,879
You dare command His Highness?

251
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,360
That's not what we're doing.

252
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,559
We simply fear a security breach.

253
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:08,519
What breach?

254
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:10,159
The Prince is checking his own property.

255
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:11,080
Where is the breach in that?

256
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,790
If a thief takes advantage
of this moment,

257
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:14,360
can you bear the responsibility?

258
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,559
Are you implying

259
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:17,559
that we are incompetent?

260
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:18,720
You...

261
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,639
After you, Your Highness.

262
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,159
Worthless fools.

263
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,080
This way, Your Highness.

264
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:44,559
Who's there?

265
00:11:45,787 --> 00:11:48,012
(Consort Duan)

266
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,559
Your Highness?

267
00:11:50,919 --> 00:11:51,919
What are you doing here?

268
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,000
I am checking
the treasures for the Prince.

269
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:55,799
Wait. Did anyone see

270
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,300
Her Highness enter the Treasure Trove?

271
00:11:57,919 --> 00:11:59,039
We've been guarding the entrance.

272
00:11:59,039 --> 00:12:00,080
No one has gone in or out.

273
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,360
Who are you, really?

274
00:12:03,710 --> 00:12:04,919
What is the meaning of this?

275
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:06,000
I am Princess Consort Duan!

276
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,919
Imposter!

277
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,000
Who are you?

278
00:12:13,225 --> 00:12:16,500
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

279
00:12:16,538 --> 00:12:19,413
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

280
00:12:19,913 --> 00:12:25,631
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

281
00:12:26,813 --> 00:12:30,133
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

282
00:12:30,537 --> 00:12:33,457
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

283
00:12:34,025 --> 00:12:39,265
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

284
00:12:40,813 --> 00:12:43,206
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

285
00:12:43,206 --> 00:12:46,856
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

286
00:12:46,925 --> 00:12:50,415
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

287
00:12:50,513 --> 00:12:53,488
♪To the ends of time♪

288
00:12:53,488 --> 00:12:56,863
♪The moon traces your face♪

289
00:12:57,050 --> 00:13:00,638
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

290
00:13:00,638 --> 00:13:06,878
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

291
00:13:07,213 --> 00:13:10,428
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

292
00:13:10,713 --> 00:13:14,251
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

293
00:13:14,538 --> 00:13:17,563
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

294
00:13:17,563 --> 00:13:20,663
♪On our way to forever♪

295
00:13:20,663 --> 00:13:24,513
♪The moon traces your face♪

296
00:13:24,513 --> 00:13:27,873
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

297
00:13:28,063 --> 00:13:34,023
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

298
00:13:35,100 --> 00:13:44,740
♪Just to be with you♪

